<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Cancelled Reservation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333333;
        }
        p {
            color: #666666;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        strong {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Reservation Cancelled</h1>
    <p>Dear Admin,</p>
    <p>This email is to inform you that a user has cancelled their reservation.</p>
    <p>Reservation Details:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>User:</strong> <%= user.name %></li>
        <li><strong>Reservation ID:</strong> <%= reservation.id %></li>
        <li><strong>Cancelled At:</strong> <%= reservation.cancelledAt %></li>
    </ul>
    <p>Please take appropriate action regarding this cancellation.</p>
    <p>If you have any questions or need further assistance, feel free to contact us.</p>
    <p>Thank you for your attention.</p>
</body>
</html>
